Uses of Class
org.oucs.gaboto.model.Gaboto

Packages that use Gaboto
org.oucs.gaboto.entities GabotoEntitys are java representations of objects from the Gaboto ontology. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.pool GabotoEntityPools are collections of GabotoEntitys. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.time While GabotoEntitys are representation of Gaboto objects at a specific point in time, GabotoTimeBasedEntity represent an Gaboto object over its lifespan. 
org.oucs.gaboto.helperscripts.importing Contains importers that can be used to load data into the Gaboto system. 
org.oucs.gaboto.model Contains the classes implementing the data model. 
org.oucs.gaboto.model.query Contains an interface to write simple predefined queries that can be transformed on the fly into various output formats. 
org.oucs.gaboto.model.query.defined Contains all predefined queries. 
org.oucs.gaboto.sample   
org.oucs.gaboto.timedim Contains classes that allow you to work with time based data.
